divs: Sighting Detailsi woke up around 4-430 in the morning and went outsidew on my patio to have a cigarete. i was walking around and happened to look up and i noticed a triangle shaped object with lights on each point in the air. i couldn't believe the way it was moveing! it was moveing north to south and it would just cut across the sky moveing left to right without makeing any kind of turn. this went on for about 4-6 minutes and then it flew off.
Summary: A triangle object with lights on each point.
